Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:14.03,ShowTitle,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:42.41,Title1,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(990,1101)}Takahashi Tetsuo Wants to Protect
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:44.45,Default - flashback,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.66,Default - flashback,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.58,Default - flashback,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,kinda arrogant, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.13,Default - flashback,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,I admit she is cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.83,Default - flashback,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,but she could hang out with \Nhim once, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.68,Default - flashback,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she thinks she's some kind of idol...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.11,BioRoom,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Biology Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.64,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:59.51,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takahashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.14,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:06.21,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's just... I heard people...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:10.77,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,s-saying mean things... about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.05,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.97,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't the place to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:17.22,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm a demi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.05,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't a demi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.15,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't feel like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.78,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.59,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't true, Kusakabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.74,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.54,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:52.02,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect this demi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:57.84,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Generally speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:02.60,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,gossip is a trivial issue, \Ncommon among high school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.12,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But since she's a demi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.56,Default - italics,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,this particular issue isn't quite that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:13.09,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari and Machi have accepted that, \Nand are living normally enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.25,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hydrangeas, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:22.26,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,There were lots of them in the garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I borrowed a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.92,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Are you working, Takahashi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:33.15,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,With the weather like this, staying in \Nthat dark prep room is depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:37.20,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I was wrong about \Nyou, Takahashi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.09,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.55,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,The thing with Machi-san's backpack...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:44.17,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to hear you asking \Nthe principal to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.36,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.88,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,You're someone so considerate of demis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:52.88,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,and on the day of the opening ceremony, \NI behaved that way toward you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:53.98,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.06,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:59.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I should apologize for being \Ninsensitive to your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.72,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,As for the backpack, Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.19,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi asked me to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.60,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san? The older sister, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.94,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I work so closely with those girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.70,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.63,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to understand them better, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.46,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.73,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.06,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:26.27,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I be of any help at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.13,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.21,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a demi, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:32.43,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've experienced that firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.45,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.53,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,A-And I'm also a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:39.62,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I have a duty to address the concerns \Nof my demi students!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:42.92,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind, I really think I can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:49.20,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:55.08,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think that sounds perfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.30,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.23,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.67,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So, the students who said mean \Nthings about Kusakabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:10.56,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they constantly gossip \Nabout others that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:14.05,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Kusakabe-san wasn't \Nbeing specifically targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:15.13,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:19.40,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,But she's convinced that it's \Nbecause she's a demi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.86,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Satou-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.66,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Even without considering the gossip,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:32.21,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-san seems to avoid contact \Nwith other people, to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.06,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, in a different way than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.76,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I get that impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.75,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,It may be that she has some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.41,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,A reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.90,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You mean something like her family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.84,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling it's more connected \Nto her nature as a demi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.01,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Her nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.90,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I had the wrong idea about you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:57.43,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,was because my succubus nature \Nmade me overly self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.57,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I see... There's that way of looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.41,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,She probably doesn't have anyone \Nto talk to about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:07.19,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,which makes it even harder to come \Nto terms with her demi identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.04,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should have tried \Nto talk to her sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.30,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't I try to speak to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.22,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to another demi \Nmight be easier for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.54,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That would be a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.69,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad you're on this with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:28.67,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-Not at all! It's just what \Nany teacher ought to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.26,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to Kusakabe is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:34.69,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But we should also deal with the \Nstudents who were gossiping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:36.23,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling them to stop won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.39,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,They don't want people to \Nknow they feel inferior,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.66,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but they're afraid to face their victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.28,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that mental weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is what makes people gossip about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.61,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like them to realize that they \Ndon't have to fall back on gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:55.74,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:05.88,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it would be unfair to expect \Nthat from high school students...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.41,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.77,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.45,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takanashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.89,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:25.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:28.80,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,And they just left it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.48,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:39.31,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Also, I heard the physics teacher, Iwai, \Nis being sent to another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:37.59,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:40.39,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yukki, I'm going to give them \Na piece of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:40.43,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Really? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.79,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.79,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He got involved in some \Nrisky stuff, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.39,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.08,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you decide what happens afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:47.31,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}With that face, maybe it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.04,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You think he went after someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.71,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,No way. He wouldn't have the guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.75,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,What a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.05,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you from class B?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.06,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.01,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.48,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Is trashing people behind their \Nbacks all you ever do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.60,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:05.75,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:08.57,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this about Kusakabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.97,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,As a fellow demi, you're out to avenge her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool of—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.32,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.03,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Yukki is a demi, but it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.77,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving you two a piece of my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because that's what I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.29,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to dodge it by provoking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.43,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to stop blabbing \Nabout people, then fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:30.13,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But every time I see or hear you doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.21,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.84,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hang around \Nand badmouth people,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.38,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,you'd better do it where I can't find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.02,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:42.96,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't the only ones who talk \Nabout people behind their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.42,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Why single us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.08,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be just you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:50.07,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give a piece of my mind to anyone \NI catch badmouthing someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.37,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so gung-ho about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.90,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone talks about people \Nbehind their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.75,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the excuse \Nthat "everyone does it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.14,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone hurts people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you think you're allowed to hurt people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.75,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you ashamed to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.87,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No one in the world likes being badmouthed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.15,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,What, so you never talk about \Nanyone behind their back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.40,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No. If I want to say something, \NI say it to their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.70,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't, I say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.06,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You think that will keep people \Nfrom talking about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.50,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.45,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I know as soon as I leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.39,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,you two will start griping about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.85,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:31.33,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It was mean of me to say it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.57,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Er, s-sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.89,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I know people who don't badmouth \Nothers still get badmouthed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.44,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, they're probably \Nthe easiest to badmouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.24,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.64,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for my satisfaction, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:49.54,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even if people say mean things about \Nme, I won't do anything I'll regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.15,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.15,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've said what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.42,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:04.95,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,I can't agree with what you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.14,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,but I am kinda impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.94,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Still, why would you say all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:12.77,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Because I promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.53,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I promised my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.19,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.72,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi Hima—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:33.88,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Ku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.23,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.21,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.09,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.48,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, things about my \Ndemi nature still bother me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:46.59,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,so I've always avoided contact with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:49.10,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,If that gave you a bad impression,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.58,Default,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.03,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who should...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.03,Default,Imori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:08.68,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.10,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The rain stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.02,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:16.20,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You hungry? I'll treat you to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.22,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:20.30,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts when you rub my head \Nwhere my hair's tied up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.61,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.67,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna rub it, rub the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.15,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:27.79,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.65,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:32.69,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.65,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where'd this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.69,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.66,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.42,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:47.99,Eyecatch,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Interviews with Monster Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.74,AVRoom,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Audiovisual Room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:53.88,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, a student came \Nto talk to me recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:58.05,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I had my own thoughts about it, \Nso I called you all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:59.25,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Satou-sensei, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.48,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone talked to you? It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.36,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:07.75,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have no tact?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.77,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:11.70,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,W-We couldn't help it! \NOnly three of us are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:17.70,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I know there are many things \Ndemis might worry about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:22.03,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for you three to be able \Nto help each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.62,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You three are the only demi \Nstudents at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:28.07,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to treasure that link among you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:31.79,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't confide in your friends, \Nyou can come to me or Satou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:36.08,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,In particular, Satou-sensei, is a demi, \Nlike you, as well as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.13,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one you can trust more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.75,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather be the one seeking advice from—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:44.74,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,F-Feel free to talk to me anytime, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.86,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:53.56,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're aware that getting together to discuss things like this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.96,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have anything they'd \Nlike to talk about right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:59.84,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can't think \Nof anything on the fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.32,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be all for today, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.14,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.82,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't gotten a hug from you yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:07.66,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:08.07,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:11.83,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.44,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Squeeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:16.80,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hee hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.25,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.60,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hee hee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.46,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha ha. Seriously, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.05,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I have one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:24.59,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:25.76,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.45,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.41,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.20,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Macchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.26,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.72,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.19,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take one, too—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.78,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's a bad idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.27,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:49.91,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.49,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Kusakabe? \NIf you'd like one, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.55,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,While we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:54.42,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.59,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,While you're at it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.08,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.46,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I won't force you to talk about \Nwhat's troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.43,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's fate that you're \Nin an environment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.93,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,where you're surrounded by other demis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:21.41,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So... I can't say it well, but I'm \Nsure it'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.06,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You will have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.11,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:25.54,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.73,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.45,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.62,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Give her a hug, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.36,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Her? But that's Machi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.15,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Just while you're at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:41.55,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... Is that all right, Machi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.58,Default,Machi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.13,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.57,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that'll be all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.76,Default,Sakie,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei, what was \Nthat weird scream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:56.93,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.34,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, wait! I have a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what that reaction meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.96,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,He called all the demis \Ntogether for a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:08.48,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Takahashi-sensei had them \Nmeet in the AV room after classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:09.99,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-sensei did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari-chan said it was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:17.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He seems pretty spacey, \Nbut he's actually very caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.17,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:19.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.54,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:28.42,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I still don't \Ntrust Takahashi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:33.03,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I got careless since it was just her \Nbody, and I hugged too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:35.09,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Machi noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.05,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.18,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:43.60,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:47.02,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know teachers were \Nallowed to leave so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.04,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.85,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,And I see you stayed pretty \Nlate, Himari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.20,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I did. I like the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.66,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I hear you did \Namazingly well on the last exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.02,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.76,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You always study in the library?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:05.39,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, and I read books to refresh myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:06.17,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.50,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing like Hikari, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.47,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,That was suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.46,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,He's always nice to Onee-chan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.34,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.55,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.31,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Just worried that my sister's \Nbeen bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:23.02,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I've been letting her cool off \Nin the biology prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.39,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.49,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you actually looking at her \Nas an experimental sample?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.28,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to prepare one for tomorrow's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.52,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I'll have enough \Nmaterials for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.02,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.88,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm overthinking this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.20,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he does love demis,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:42.48,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way he thinks about the nature \Nof vampires around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.48,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you something \Nabout the nature of vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.25,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,He actually does!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.00,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.23,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari seems to have no problem \Nchowing down on garlic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.64,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but the stories you hear posit \Nthat vampires hate garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.56,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about whether it was all fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.40,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.69,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,They say vampires attack humans at \Nnight, under cover of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:03.71,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.66,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, isn't it because they hate sunlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:10.15,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that makes them scary \Nenough for people to carry crosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:14.42,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Some texts say that vampires \Nhave very keen senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.24,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:20.24,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Sharp vision, even at night, \Nhearing that can detect humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.47,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,a sharp sense of smell to pick \Nup the scent of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:26.25,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than enough for an \Nadvantage over humans in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:29.61,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,What does the sharpness of their \Nsenses have to do with garlic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:32.14,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the key point is their sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:35.84,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Since their noses are so sensitive, \Nthey hate strong-smelling foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:40.46,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's why vampires \Nin legends hate garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.49,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about those things, \Nbut what's the real story?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:46.02,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Does Hikari have sharp senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.73,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's an accurate perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.58,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's senses are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.06,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:55.38,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how can she eat so much garlic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.28,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:00.13,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,She just isn't picky enough about her food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:04.32,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I got concerned and asked her if \Nshe was forcing herself to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.16,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,And she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.98,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:10.04,Default - flashback,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I love foods that smell really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.39,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want her to say that in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.80,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.91,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of people who talk to \Nme about my sister say
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.02,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,she doesn't seem like a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:26.43,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,that she's just like a\Nnormal high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:30.85,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You seem very interested in demis' natures,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.31,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,so what do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:35.48,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think my sister doesn't \Nseem like a vampire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:39.32,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not that interested \Nin her human side?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.79,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll give you a straight answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:47.86,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that she doesn't behave \Nthe way I'd expect a vampire to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:50.60,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But if you asked whether that \Nmakes her unlike a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.96,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.92,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari does want to suck people's blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.17,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but she settles for blood bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.67,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,And even though she has a vampire's \Nkeen sense of smell,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.03,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,she loves foods with strong scents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:07.82,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That human side is what \Nmakes her like a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.43,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,and it's what makes her unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.42,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't how you're born that \Nmakes you "like" something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.31,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It's how you live with what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.61,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean it's okay to neglect \Nan understanding of a demi's nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:23.11,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The concerns unique to demis \Nare caused by their natures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.12,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You can't look at things in only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.58,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You should look from both angles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.33,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If you just see traits unique to demis, \Nyou'll miss their individuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.53,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If you only see the human side, \Nyou won't understand their troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.02,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Both are precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.59,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:39.46,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.47,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.14,Default - italics,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can trust him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:48.71,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:50.02,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.74,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come \Nto our house sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.73,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I did, not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of it, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.94,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like my parents to hear \Nwhat you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:00.98,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:05.74,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was thinking I'd like \Nto talk to your parents, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.92,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.45,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, I have a question for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:14.23,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,What does hugging my sister let you learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:17.04,Writing,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}Sensei hugged me today! \NHe totally attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:18.29,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Was it her vampire nature, \Nor her human side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:21.42,SignA,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shibasaki Station
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.74,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Hugged? Attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.09,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong, Himari-chan! \NShe's the one who—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.22,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:29.26,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Rationalizing, demi-loving teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.35,Default,Tetsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deny that, but still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:33.35,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:34.83,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, are you oka—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:39.73,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,And why send me such \Na misleading message?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.32,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:45.26,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You were so late getting home,\N and I was bored here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:49.68,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I sent a message like \Nthat, you'd come home faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:51.41,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea Sensei was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:58.42,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd just sent a message asking \Nme to hurry home, I would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:01.29,Default,Hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I love you, Himari!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.63,Default,Himari,0000,0000,0000,,Quit clinging to me!
